data.description: Open House (Sat-Sun) Nov 4th & 5th 11-2. Welcome to 6003 Pleasant Lake, a captivating two-story traditional brick house that embodies classic charm and modern comfort. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this home offers a spacious backyard and a well-thought-out floor plan, making it ideal for everyone! As you approach the property, the timeless brick exterior exudes an inviting warmth that welcomes you home. Inside, the home unfolds with a thoughtful layout, creating a comfortable and functional living space. The bedrooms have been carefully designed to provide ample room for relaxation and personalization, ensuring everyone can enjoy their own private retreat. The bathrooms offer modern convenience and style, providing a touch of luxury to your daily routines. Whether you're getting ready for the day or winding down in the evening. One of the standout features of this property is the spacious backyard. It's a versatile canvas where you can let your imagination run wild. Create a lush garden oasis, set up an outdoor entertainment area, or simply let the kids and pets roam free in this expansive outdoor space. Located in a desirable San Antonio neighborhood, you'll have easy access to local amenities, schools, and parks. Plus, with a convenient location, commuting to various parts of the city is a breeze. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home. Experience the perfect blend of classic charm, modern amenities, and outdoor freedom in this lovely two-story brick house. Schedule a viewing today!
